type prosakart in terminal/konsole to launch the program

The workflow to create a test is confusing at first. First i had to create two languages. than i had to create a sheet. The sheet is some kind of set of questions. then create the questions. make sure the questions are attache to a sheet, otherwise they would show up.
 you can create several correct answers. this was good for me, because the answers are case sensitive, but i don't bother.

i learnd the NATO alphabet with it and i'm happy about.
summary: type prosakart into terminal to open. minimalistic
